<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/brucewu0463" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5526785); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5526785&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610200723" alt="BruceWu0463" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5526785)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/brucewu0463" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5526785); return false;">BruceWu0463</a></span></p>
